<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> trust someone for something • trust someone with something</xh5><p> <i>trust someone for something—</i>allow credit for smth. such as goods to a customer: Can you <u>trust me for</u> a packet of cigarettes until Friday.</p><p> <i>trust someone with something—</i>give a person the care of smth. with complete confidence: I’ve <u>trusted him with</u> everything I have—money, house, horses.</p> </entry>
